data.description: TRU Bankers Hill is a brand new community that opened in July 2021! With our prime location, find yourself within walking distance of Balboa Park, Little Italy, Hillcrest and more! Our pet friendly community is located at the corner of 4th Avenue and Grape Street, with our very own coffee shop on the ground floor brought to you by Mostra Coffee! Our leasing office is remote and offers tours by appointment only. If you wish to tour a unit, please contact our leasing office directly. Additional walk through videos can be found on our YouTube channel. Inquire for more information!
